{"article_id":"P7XAN5xgxvjNX172","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Calls for Virginia Gov . Ralph Northam to resign are coming from all sides of the political aisle","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"following the report Friday","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"that Northam appeared in a photo in his medical school yearbook","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"that showed a man","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"dressed in blackface and another person","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"wearing a Ku Klux Klan robe and hood .","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"Northam apologized Friday","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"and vowed to mend the damage","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"he 'd caused with the photograph .","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"But he reversed himself Saturday ,","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"he does not believe","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"he appears in the racist photo","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"as he initially thought .","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"The photo was included on Northam 's yearbook page from Eastern Virginia Medical School in 1984 .","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"More :","depth":4},{"id":16,"text":"' I am not the person in that photo ' :","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"Virginia Gov . Ralph Northam denies","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"he was in racist image","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"The calls","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"for him to step aside","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"only heightened on Saturday ,","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"with President Donald Trump along with some of the nation 's top Democrats condemning the Virginia Democrat .","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"Trump wrote in a tweet","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"that Northam 's actions were `` Unforgivable ! '' `` Democrat Governor Ralph Northam of Virginia just stated ,","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"\" I believe","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"that I am not either of the people in that photo. \"","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"This was 24 hours after apologizing","depth":13},{"id":28,"text":"for appearing in the picture","depth":13},{"id":29,"text":"and after making the most horrible statement on \" super \" late term abortion . '' `` There is no place for racism in America , ''","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"former Vice President Joe Biden wrote on Twitter .","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"`` Governor Northam has lost all moral authority","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"and should resign immediately ,","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"Justin Fairfax is the leader","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"Virginia needs now . ''","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"House Speaker Nancy Pelosi , the top Democrat in Washington , said on Saturday","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"that Northam should leave office","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"so those in his state could heal","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"and move forward .","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"`` The photo is racist","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"and contrary to fundamental American values , ''","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"Pelosi said in a tweet .","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"`` I join my colleagues in Virginia","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"calling on Governor Northam to do the right thing","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"so that the people of the Commonwealth of Virginia can heal","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"and move forward . ''","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"The NAACP 's President and CEO Derrick Johnson agreed in a written statement ,","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"saying ,","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"`` Black face in any manner is always racist and never okay .","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"No matter the party affiliation , we can not stand for such behavior ,","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"which is why the NAACP is calling for the resignation of Virginia Gov . Ralph Northam . ''","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"Republicans and Democrats ,","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"including nearly every Democratic presidential contender in the 2020 race ,","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"joined together","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"to call for his resignation .","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"`` It doesn ' t matter if he is a Republican or a Democrat .","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"This behavior was racist and unconscionable .","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"Governor Northam should resign , ''","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"Julian Castro , a Democrat","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"running for president ,","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"wrote on Twitter .","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"`` Leaders are called to a higher standard ,","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"and the stain of racism should have no place in the halls of government , ''","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"she wrote on Twitter .","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"`` The Governor of Virginia should step aside","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"so the public can heal","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"and move forward together .","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"Sen. Tim Scott , a Republican from South Carolina","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"who recently spoke out against Rep. Steve King 's remarks about white supremacism ,","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"also denounced Northam 's yearbook fiasco .","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"`` To be clear ,","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"while a quick apology is good ,","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"it does not excuse the choices","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"made by @ GovernorVA as an adult","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"enrolled in medical school , ''","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"Scott wrote on Twitter .","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"`` The people of VA will make their voices heard ;","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"I hope","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"they will shout far & wide","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"that there are consequences for such showcases of prejudice & hate . ''","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"Sens . Mark Warner and Tim Kaine , both former Virginia governors , released a statement along with U.S. Rep. Bobby Scott , D-Va. ,","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"after watching Northam 's press conference Saturday :","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"\" We called Governor Northam","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"to tell him","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"that we no longer believe","depth":14},{"id":85,"text":"he can effectively serve as Governor of Virginia","depth":14},{"id":86,"text":"and that he must resign .","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"The events of the past 24 hours have inflicted immense pain","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"and irrevocably broken the trust","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"Virginians must have in their leaders . \"","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"New Jersey Gov . Phil Murphy spoke out on `` All in with Chris Hayes '' on MSNBC Friday night .","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"`` We ' re the party of Barack Obama ,","depth":13},{"id":92,"text":"we ' re the party of inclusion , ''","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"Murphy said .","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"Murphy described it as unacceptable behavior in 2019 ,","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"and that it was just as unacceptable in 1984 .","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"The incoming head of the Democratic Governors Association , Murphy said","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"he speaks of Northam 's yearbook controversy with a `` heavy heart . ''","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"`` I know him","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"and I believe","depth":13},{"id":100,"text":"he 's a good man , ''","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"New Jersey 's governor said .","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"Planned Parenthood tweeted a statement late Friday night","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"telling Northam to resign .","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"Hillary Clinton , the 2016 Democratic presidential nominee , also weighed in ,","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"saying in a Saturday night tweet ,","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"`` This has gone on too long .","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"There is nothing","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"to debate .","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"He must resign . ''","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"Members of the Virginia Legislative Black Caucus said Friday","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"they are `` still processing '' the news .","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"In a statement","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"issued Friday night ,","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"the caucus said","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"`` what has been revealed is disgusting , reprehensible , and offensive . ''","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"It went on to say","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"while the caucus has `` no permanent friends , no permanent enemies , only permanent interests ,","depth":12},{"id":119,"text":"'' members `` are still processing what we have seen about the Governor . ''","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"Mark Herring said in a statement Saturday","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"that it ' s no longer possible for Northam to \" lead our Commonwealth . \"","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"The revelation of the yearbook photo comes at a particularly partisan time in Virginia .","depth":3},{"id":123,"text":"The state has been battling over a Democratic-led bill","depth":4},{"id":124,"text":"that would loosen restrictions on late-term abortions ,","depth":5},{"id":125,"text":"allowing a woman to get an abortion well into the third trimester","depth":6},{"id":126,"text":"if the mother was physically or mentally at risk .","depth":6},{"id":127,"text":"This week the bill failed to be voted out of committee","depth":3},{"id":128,"text":"but the uproar has n't stopped .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":257,"left":250,"right":256,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":250,"left":143,"right":249,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":143,"left":0,"right":142,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":142,"left":133,"right":141,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":133,"left":1,"right":132,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":2,"right":131,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":131,"left":3,"right":130,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"ela